"" "Hold home key Action" "||" "Game Switcher|In-game menu|Exit game" "$HELP$ get hold_home 'Game Switcher'" "$HELP$ update hold_home 'Game Switcher'|$HELP$ update hold_home 'In-game menu'|$HELP$ update hold_home 'Exit game'" ""
